snippet.title: A Summer with the Shiba Inu   Steam Greenlight Trailer
snippet.description:
New trailer out now! https://youtu.be/4hUY2DodmYc

Get it on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/916030/A_Summer_with_the_Shiba_Inu/

Syd the Shiba Inu quits her job in Canine-da, and goes to fight other dogs on an Island. What could go wrong? Your choices matter - there are multiple drastic ways to change the fate of Shiba Island, with 10+ variants depending on how you treat the dogs you meet along the way.

Platforms: Windows PC

Website: http://www.quill-studios.com/a-summer-with-the-shiba-inu

Music: http://www.purple-planet.com
